        "correct": "floatBot > 0",
        "label": "'C'",
        "why": "floatBot > 0 ? ('Float ' + (lsC - 0) + ' (LS ' + lsC + ' ≠ ES 0) — off the critical path.') : 'Zero float — on the critical path.'"
      },
      {
        "id": "'D'",
        "x": 170,
        "y": 140,
        "w": 58,
        "h": 46,
        "correct": "floatBot > 0",
        "label": "'D'",
        "why": "floatBot > 0 ? ('Float ' + (lsD - efC) + ' (LS ' + lsD + ' ≠ ES ' + efC + ') — off the critical path.') : 'Zero float — on the critical path.'"
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "Path A→B = {{p1}}, path C→D = {{p2}}. The longer path {{longer}} is critical (zero float); the two activities on the shorter path {{shorter}} each carry {{slack}} day{{slack==1 ? '' : 's'}} of float."
  }
]
